Package org.rogatio.circlead.control.synchronizer

Class SynchronizerFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rogatio.circlead.control.synchronizer.SynchronizerFactory
  • public final class SynchronizerFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    A factory for holding Synchronizer objects. Is solved as singleton-class, so it can be used from the whole application. Must be initialized before reading or saving data from repository.

      • getSynchronizerByPattern

        public ISynchronizer getSynchronizerByPattern​(java.lang.String id)
        Gets the synchronizer by id pattern. Uses #getIdPattern(). Works only when synchronizers have all different id-patterns.
        Parameters:
        id - the id of a workitem
        Returns:
        the synchronizer which could handle the id as valid (by pattern)
